results.name: Decimal expansion of the speed c/a in SI units [meter/second], where "c" is the speed of light in vacuum and "a" is the fine-structure constant (alpha).
comment: Also phase velocity of de Broglie wave of a particle whose velocity is equal to the Bohr N1 velocity (A081800).
Note that this speed is greater than c.
results.author: _Omar E. Pol_, Nov 07 2013
